      • cut

        public FeatureTable cut(int from,
               int to)
        Description copied from interface: FeatureTable
        Cut a feature table given new from and to values. Given from and to values, all features located outside the range are discarded, all features located fully within the range are conserved, as well as all features spanning from and/or to values. For the latter case, feature's coordinates are updated to fit within the range. Please provide a from value always less than to value. If the feature table is out of range given the new coordinates, then this method return null.
        Specified by:
        cut in interface FeatureTable
